title: Desktop.Icon.Toy.1.0-miniyou
description:
Name: Desktop Icon Toy 1.0
Sys req: Windows, unsure about Vista compability. Try...

This is really a toy. With this program

Windows desktop, like arrange all the icons

arranged like a clock - synchronized with
your system. For more info, check iDeskSoft&#039;s
homepage at <a href="
http://www.idesksoft.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.idesksoft.com/</a>




Originally released on TPB by miniyou,
but I couldn&#039;t care less about what you do
with it as long as you keep seeding until
you have a nice ratio.
